# Title: Decode Base64 Encoded Text -MacOs
# Author: Daniil Yugoslavskiy, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-19
# Level: low
# Description: Detects usage of base64 utility to decode arbitrary base64-encoded text
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/macos/process_creation/proc_creation_macos_base64_decode.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate activities

CommandLine="*-d*" Image="/usr/bin/base64"